@aditigolf Hi @aditigolf, we sincerely apologize for this situation and the inconvenience it causes. Our customer service is doing everything possible to get your luggage to your final destination as soon as possible, as requested during your private conversation with them.
Regards,
Jimmy

@Tmporterjr Hi Thomas ! 
We're really sorry about this delay which is due to the late arrival of the incoming aircraft and the waiting for a stand-by crew from Paris. The flight left CDG at 16h11LT and will depart from AMS at 17h40LT. Follow your flight here https://t.co/gRGzVkU7Yh. 
Anne

@emohit We sincerely apologize for the delay. Could you please contact us via Messenger  https://t.co/wnNppLybFB ?
Best Regards.
Patricia

@aliciaramirezs2 Hola Alicia, gracias por comunicarnos por este medio.

Nos podrías enviar un DM con tu número de PIR que aeropuerto te ya indicado.

